properties.Name: ProductLifecycleEventType
properties.Description:
A type of lifecycle event that may be associated to a Product.

Ex:
- Product Introduction
- Product First Sales
- Product First Installation
- Product Abandonment Announced
- Product Abandonment
- Product Discontinued
- Product Engineering Update
- Product Recall

Columns.Name: ProductLifecycleEventTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product Lifecycle Event Type.

Columns.Name: ProductLifecycleEventTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Product Lifecycle Event Type.

Columns.Name: ProductLifecycleEventTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Product Lifecycle Event Type.
